      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior has no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The interior shows no wear on the upholstery, trim, or surfaces. All mechanical systems are fully functional and operating as expected. A clean, well-maintained vehicle with nothing to hide.",
